? I try to approach the tree that is distrustfully fleeing, to cultivate and make our common future better.", "short_description": "An ecological catastrophe. Everything is black carbon. Is that all? There it is, a single plant fights and survives successfully \u2026 Which plant is it? How did it survive? Let\u2019s see here, let\u2019s get closer to it \u2026 "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://virtualunit.org/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VirutalUnit", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://virtualunit.org/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ART_CREATIVITY", "EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "422138876354863"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "177568181118090"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "177568181118090"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1631046780, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "177568181118090"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "4359569517497162", "version": "0.1"}, "id": "1133896623765470", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4188524877934961", "is_concept": false, "latest